
====================================
            HOW TO RUN
====================================

1. Run the server Jar on any internet connected pc.

2. Run the client on another pc and follow the on screen instructions.

3. The client must enter a username and the IP it is attempting to connect to.

4. Upon connecting, the client needs to wait for the server to enter the private key.

5. After the private key is sent(RSA) the client then needs to wait for the admin to enter the IV.

6. After this client is connected, same thing everytime.


The server will relay every message it recieves to all connected clients. It's display shows the ciphertext.

